    <item>
      <title>日本央行结束负利率时代，几乎没有进一步加息的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行结束了现代历史上最激进的货币刺激计划，废除了世界上最后一次负利率，同时暂时保持宽松的金融状况——在做出广泛预期的决定后，鸽派基调削弱了日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-ends-massive-easing-program-with-first-rate-hike-since-2007</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行 17 年来首次加息，日元下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行结束了世界上最后一次负利率，这是人们普遍预期的举措，同时暂时保持宽松的金融状况，导致日元走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
